Subject: [LTO] add static-plugin registration hook for downstream linkers

Adds an opt-in function-pointer hook so a downstream linker can register
statically-linked pass plugins with the LTO PassBuilder without needing
dlopen-able .so/.dll files, plus a static OptPipeline fallback so a linker
with no --lto-newpm-passes (lld-link) can still force a pass pipeline.
When unset (default), behaviour is identical to upstream.

